right&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;18&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;100&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0.002&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Fatehpur Sikri (5 of 18)\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/fatehpur-sikri-5-of-181.jpg?w=1024&#038;h=584?w=450\" data-large-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/fatehpur-sikri-5-of-181.jpg?w=1024&#038;h=584?w=700\" class=\" size-full wp-image-2555 aligncenter\" src=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/fatehpur-sikri-5-of-181.jpg?w=1024&#038;h=584\" alt=\"Fatehpur Sikri (5 of 18)\" width=\"1024\" height=\"584\" srcset=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/fatehpur-sikri-5-of-181.jpg 1024w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/fatehpur-sikri-5-of-181.jpg?w=150&amp;h=86 150w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/fatehpur-sikri-5-of-181.jpg?w=450&amp;h=257 450w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/fatehpur-sikri-5-of-181.jpg?w=768&amp;h=438 768w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/fatehpur-sikri-5-of-181.jpg?w=700&amp;h=399 700w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\">Jodha Bai&#8217;s palace</figcaption></figure>\n<figure data-shortcode=\"caption\" id=\"attachment_2562\" style=\"width: 1024px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"2562\" data-permalink=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.wordpress.com/2016/02/08/agra-the-mughal-capital/fatehpur-sikri-8-of-18/\" data-orig-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/fatehpur-sikri-8-of-181.jpg?w=1024&#038;h=576\" data-orig-size=\"1024,576\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;22&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Nabhoneel Majumdar&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;Canon EOS REBEL T3&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1446568883&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;18&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;400&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0.025&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Fatehpur Sikri (8 of 18)\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/fatehpur-sikri-8-of-181.jpg?w=1024&#038;h=576?w=450\" data-large-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/fatehpur-sikri-8-of-181.jpg?w=1024&#038;h=576?w=700\" class=\" size-full wp-image-2562 aligncenter\" src=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/fatehpur-sikri-8-of-181.jpg?w=1024&#038;h=576\" alt=\"Fatehpur Sikri (8 of 18)\" width=\"1024\" height=\"576\" srcset=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/fatehpur-sikri-8-of-181.jpg 1024w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/fatehpur-sikri-8-of-181.jpg?w=150&amp;h=84 150w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/fatehpur-sikri-8-of-181.jpg?w=450&amp;h=253 450w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/fatehpur-sikri-8-of-181.jpg?w=768&amp;h=432 768w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/fatehpur-sikri-8-of-181.jpg?w=700&amp;h=394 700w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\">Buland Darwaza</figcaption></figure>\n<p><img data-attachment-id=\"2558\" data-permalink=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.wordpress.com/2016/02/08/agra-the-mughal-capital/fatehpur-sikri-18-of-18/\" data-orig-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/fatehpur-sikri-18-of-181.jpg?w=431&#038;h=600\" data-orig-size=\"431,600\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;5.6&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Nabhoneel Majumdar&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;Canon EOS REBEL T3&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1446568364&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;47&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;100&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0.033333333333333&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Fatehpur Sikri (18 of 18)\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/fatehpur-sikri-18-of-181.jpg?w=431&#038;h=600?w=323\" data-large-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/fatehpur-sikri-18-of-181.jpg?w=431&#038;h=600?w=431\" class=\" size-full wp-image-2558 aligncenter\" src=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/fatehpur-sikri-18-of-181.jpg?w=431&#038;h=600\" alt=\"Fatehpur Sikri (18 of 18)\" width=\"431\" height=\"600\" srcset=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/fatehpur-sikri-18-of-181.jpg 431w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/fatehpur-sikri-18-of-181.jpg?w=108&amp;h=150 108w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 431px) 100vw, 431px\" /></p>\n<p><img data-attachment-id=\"2560\" data-permalink=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.wordpress.com/2016/02/08/agra-the-mughal-capital/fatehpur-sikri-7-of-18/\" data-orig-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/fatehpur-sikri-7-of-181.jpg?w=600&#038;h=600\" data-orig-size=\"600,600\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;5.6&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Nabhoneel Majumdar&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;Canon EOS REBEL T3&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1446568837&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;55&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;100&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0.003125&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Fatehpur Sikri (7 of 18)\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/fatehpur-sikri-7-of-181.jpg?w=600&#038;h=600?w=450\" data-large-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/fatehpur-sikri-7-of-181.jpg?w=600&#038;h=600?w=600\" class=\" size-full wp-image-2560 aligncenter\" src=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/fatehpur-sikri-7-of-181.jpg?w=600&#038;h=600\" alt=\"Fatehpur Sikri (7 of 18)\" width=\"600\" height=\"600\" srcset=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/fatehpur-sikri-7-of-181.jpg 600w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/fatehpur-sikri-7-of-181.jpg?w=150&amp;h=150 150w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/fatehpur-sikri-7-of-181.jpg?w=450&amp;h=450 450w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">The area behind the Buland Darwaza contains the Tomb of Sheikh Salim Chisti.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Chisti had blessed Akbar soon after which he had had three sons.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Akbar had Fatehpur Sikri built around his camp. Nowadays, people believe that offering prayers at the <em>mazar </em>(mausoleum) fulfils whatever one wishes.</p>\n<hr />\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">We had barely covered one-third of the fort. It is <em>huge. </em>It is lively. It is something to be witnessed, but it requires an entire day.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">In short, we covered (very briefly) two places in Agra on the 3rd of November, which are two of the finest examples of Mughal architecture.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n","date":"2016-02-08T16:05:03.000Z","slug":"agra-the-mughal-capital","excerpt":"<p>Fatehpur Sikri&#8217;s grandeur can still be witnessed by tourists.<br />\nThe once abandoned city-fort is as lively as it had been in the 1850s.</p>\n","jetpack_featured_media_url":"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/fatehpur-sikri-1-of-1.jpg"},"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Nabhoneel's Parchments","subtitle":"All thing photographed and written down"}}},"pageContext":{"id":"5ab5d43e-5b51-50db-bcff-6806e70cbb6d"}}